  "subject": "Add GlusterFS Support to ONAP",
  "commit_message": "Add GlusterFS Support to ONAP\n\nThis draft submission adds the following:\nCustom values file for enabling and disabling glusterfs persistent\nstorage on per component basis.\nCustom script \"deploy_glusterfs.bash\" to deploy Glusterfs infrastructure\n in Openstack/Rancher environment. To do: able to specify namespace\n(currently deploys to default)\nCustom script \"cleanup_gluster.bash\" to cleanup gluster infrastructure\n after onap helm chart has been deleted.\nModifications to the subcharts are required to get gluster working on\neach component. This will be added in subsequent check-ins.\n\nChange-Id: Ibce8ce63d4e712013b93c9b0d42091d4a9a5c0cb\nIssue-ID: OOM-1228\nSigned-off-by: slanthie <slanthie@amdocs.com>\n",
